        "question": "Evaluate $ \\lim_{x \\to 3} \\frac{x^2 - 9}{x - 3} $",
        "options": ["3", "6", "0", "Does not exist"],
        "answer": "B",
        "explanation": "Factor numerator: $(x-3)(x+3)$. Cancel $(x-3)$: $x+3 \\to 3+3 = 6$"
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Evaluate $ \\lim_{x \\to 0} \\frac{\\sin(6x)}{\\tan(2x)} $",
        "options": ["3", "2", "1", "0"],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$\\frac{\\sin(6x)}{\\tan(2x)} = \\frac{\\sin(6x)}{\\sin(2x)} \\cdot \\cos(2x) = \\frac{6x}{2x} \\cdot 1 = 3$"
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Evaluate $ \\lim_{x \\to 4} \\frac{\\sqrt{x} - 2}{x - 4} $",
