        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "Multiply by conjugate: $\\frac{(\\sqrt{x} - 2)}{(\\sqrt{x} - 2)(\\sqrt{x} + 2)} = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{x} + 2} \\to \\frac{1}{4}$"
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Evaluate $ \\lim_{x \\to 0} \\frac{1 - \\cos(8x)}{x \\sin(4x)} $",
