        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$\\frac{e^{5x} - 1}{2x} = \\frac{5}{2} \\cdot \\frac{e^{5x} - 1}{5x} \\to \\frac{5}{2} \\cdot 1 = \\frac{5}{2}$"
      },
