        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "Factor numerator: $(x-1)(x^2 + x + 1)$, denominator: $(x-1)(x+1)$. Cancel: $\\frac{x^2 + x + 1}{x+1} \\to \\frac{3}{2}$"
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Evaluate $ \\lim_{x \\to 0} \\frac{\\ln(1 + 4x)}{x} $",
