        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$\\frac{\\sin(7x) - \\sin(3x)}{x} = 7 \\cdot \\frac{\\sin(7x)}{7x} - 3 \\cdot \\frac{\\sin(3x)}{3x} \\to 7 - 3 = 4$"
      },
