        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "Factor numerator: $x(x^2 - 4x + 4) = x(x-2)^2$, denominator: $(x-2)(x+2)$. Cancel one $(x-2)$: $\\frac{x(x-2)}{x+2} \\to \\frac{2 \\cdot 0}{4} = 0$"
      }
